<h1 class="entry-title">1<sup>st</sup> Source Contractors</h1>
<div class="entry-content">
<img src="/wp-content/uploads/residential-roofing-contractor.jpg" class="phright" alt="St. Louis Roofing Contractor" />
<p>For expert help with <a href="/roofing/" title="Roofing">roofing</a>, <a href="/siding/" title="Siding">siding</a> and <a href="/gutters/" title="Gutters">gutters</a>, call 1st Source Contractors. We are experienced and uniquely certified to solve all your home improvement dilemmas, and storm repair is our specialty. Call our friendly team now to arrange a free estimate.</p>
<p>Our team serves the greater St. Louis and Quad Cities areas, helping families and business owners recover from weather disasters and make everyday home improvement decisions. Our focus is embodied by our motto: "To deliver the best product and customer service to each of our customers at all times."</p>
<ul class="doubleul">
<li><a href="/roofing/roof-repair/" title="Roof Repair St. Louis">Roof Repair</a></li>
<li><a href="/roofing/roof-replacement/" title="Roof Replacement St. Louis">Roof Replacement</a></li>
<li><a href="/roofing/new-roof/" title="New Roof">New Roofs</a></li>
<li><a href="/siding/siding-repair/" title="Siding Repair St. Louis">Siding Repair</a></li>
<li><a href="/siding/siding-replacement/" title="Siding Replacement St. Louis">Siding Replacement</a></li>
</ul>
<ul class="doubleul" style="margin-right:0;">
<li><a href="/siding/new-siding/" title="New Siding">New Siding</a></li>
<li><a href="/gutters/gutter-repair/" title="Gutter Repair St. Louis">Gutter Repair</a></li>
<li><a href="/gutters/gutter-replacement/" title="Gutter Replacement St. Louis">Gutter Replacement</a></li>
<li><a href="/gutters/new-gutters/" title="New Gutters">New Gutters</a></li>
<li><a href="/insurance-claims/" title="Insurance Claims">Insurance Claims</a></li>
</ul>
<div class="clear"></div>
<p><span class="bold">A Leading, Local Roofing Company</span><br />
We have been doing this work for more than a decade, and will be around now and in the future for all your roof and gutter needs. We are a GAF Master Elite Contractor (only 3% of roofers carry this distinction), and a CertainTeed Master Shingle Company. We also install Owens Corning, Tamko, Atlas, and other top name brands.</p>
<p>Our membership in the National Roofing Contractors Association assures you of our uncompromising standards, and our A+ rating with the BBB assures you of our dedication to customer satisfaction. We stand behind our work!</p>
<p><span class="bold">Roof Repair and Replacement</span><br />
Roof damage can be easy to spot or cause damage months or years down the road. We have the experience and knowledge to assess all roof types quickly and make the necessary repairs within your budget.</p>
<p>Call right away if you have visible damage. Hailstones can knock protective granules off of shingles, crack slates and pit metal. Wind can lift the edges of almost any surface or pummel it with debris. When you call us for help you get prompt service and clear, written estimates. We can put an emergency tarp over punctured areas and then do the needed repairs.</p>
<p>Even if you don't see any damage, you should call us for an inspection to make sure. It's free and without obligation. Moisture could get inside and cause a number of problems: rotten building materials, pest infestations and mold. And remember that if you wait too long, your insurance company could deny that your claim was related to a specific storm.</p>
<p><span class="bold">Insurance Help is Here</span><br />
A big source of stress after a storm involves dealing with insurance companies. Don’t add to your worries. Call us. We work with the insurers all the time to help homeowners seek coverage of weather-related damage. Our trained staff can be there to inspect the rooftop with your adjuster so nothing is missed, including hail damage to gutter and siding installations. We can help get your paperwork in order, or handle the entire process for you.</p>
<p><span class="bold">New Roof Replacement</span><br />
Do you need residential or commercial roof replacement? We specialize in these roof types: asphalt composition, standing seam metal, slate, cedar and low-sloped coverings. Every part of the system will be installed to local building codes including underlayment and decking, flashings, ventilation, and new gutter systems.</p>
<p>Whenever possible, we try to repair your surface. But if the damage is too extensive or you face repeated repairs, we will discuss replacement options with you. Count on us to tell it to you straight.</p>
<img src="/wp-content/uploads/residential-siding-contractor.jpg" class="phleft" alt="Home Siding St. Louis" />
<p><span class="bold">Home Siding Replacement and Repair</span><br />
Siding completes the look of a house. The right kind can also bolster your house against wind and hail, add an insulation layer, and provide you with low-maintenance beauty. We offer only top name products in aluminum, metal, vinyl and fiber cement. Check out attractive new siding types from trusted brands like James Hardie, Alside, Crane and Mastic.</p>
<p>If yours is damaged, our technicians can do prompt siding repair or install closely-matching replacement panels.</p>
<p><span class="bold">Gutter Repair and Replacement</span><br />
Gutters that are properly attached and free of clogs will keep water running off of your roof and away from your foundation. Chances are yours are old, degraded or undersized. Count on us to make the right repairs or replace them with long-lasting aluminum or elegant copper gutter types. This is one investment that you can't take for granted. We’ll give you a free, fair estimate for new gutter replacement.</p>
<p><span class="bold">Serving Those Who Serve Our Country</span><br />
We are proud supporters of our active and retired military community, and participate in GAF's Roofs for Troops program. Ask us about money-saving mail-in rebates on select new roof installations.</p>
<p>Whether you need a roof repair, new siding or more dependable gutters, make your first call to 1st Source Contractors. We proudly serve St. Louis, O'Fallon, Belleville, Fairview Heights and all surrounding areas.</p><br />
</div>
